                        <condition>
                           <list>
                              <item>
                                 <p>Paper, about 9 1/8 in. by 6 1/2, consisting of 58 leaves, some
                                    of which are much stained and torn, especially foll. 1, 9, 29,
                                    30, 33—35, 39 —42, 47, 49, 50, and 58. The quires, signed with
                                    letters, were originally upwards of 18 in number (<foreign xml:lang="syr">ܝܚ</foreign>, fol. 50 a); but many of them are
                                    lost, and most of the remainder are very imperfect. Leaves are
                                    now wanting at the beginning and end, as well as after foll.28,
                                    34, 35, 40, 48, and 49. There are 14 lines in each page.</p>
                              </item>
                           </list>
                        </condition>
                     </supportDesc>
                  </objectDesc>
